::IsCSSEnabled().\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D4304", "files": ["editor/libeditor/HTMLEditor.h", "editor/libeditor/HTMLEditorDocumentCommands.cpp", "editor/libeditor/HTMLStyleEditor.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "71525c253ed0c6fb711f99e13de8d6d6e54a6a4a", "parents": ["fb811847c1e42298213f26283225e062cf2df3c2"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mark Hammond \u003cmhammond@skippinet.com.au\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1483017 - ensure Sync is initialized before disconnecting. r=tcsc\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8987f26wH16\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D4276", "files": ["services/sync/modules/SyncDisconnect.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "66fb08227855c12a5362dc9027a3bddf125b6c39", "parents": ["71525c253ed0c6fb711f99e13de8d6d6e54a6a4a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Hiroyuki Ikezoe \u003chikezoe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1475462 - Implement prefers-reduced-motion for MacOSX. r=mstange\n\nThe local declaration part was done by jfkthame.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D4499", "files": ["widget/cocoa/nsLookAndFeel.mm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0c635c42c13c59c5fa2b291a5d32e3edecd73a2f", "parents": ["66fb08227855c12a5362dc9027a3bddf125b6c39"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Chris Manchester \u003ccmanchester@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1485184 - Bump enforced upper rustc version limit. r=glandium\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D4036", "files": ["toolkit/library/rust/shared/build.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "99cfa5bb259e0fdf1b3d4c90cce959b00d1394e3", "parents": ["0c635c42c13c59c5fa2b291a5d32e3edecd73a2f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Chris Manchester \u003ccmanchester@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1485184 - Update the rust-nightly toolchain task to the most recent