l], "node": "29b5c763db4544c1d7449f12357ba1c588754a73", "parents": ["822408e3c78d084615237e1de4c124a9db9da963"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daosheng Mu \u003cdaoshengmu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1488573 - Part 1: Add crash log for VR controllers have unmatched button/axis count. r=kip a=pascalc\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8F3cDiZJ7ef\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D6817", "files": ["gfx/vr/gfxVROculus.cpp", "gfx/vr/gfxVROpenVR.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "90aae1fda3666fcfba41a833fa4a278a6dae3b2d", "parents": ["29b5c763db4544c1d7449f12357ba1c588754a73"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daosheng Mu \u003cdaoshengmu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1488573 - Part 2: Checking OpenVR btn/axis count at runtime to avoid array overflow. r=kip a=pascalc\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 5KgcuAcKCmO\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D6744", "files": ["gfx/vr/gfxVROpenVR.cpp", "gfx/vr/gfxVROpenVR.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3c7440cdf2d58848df8aeece6e31aab206c16098", "parents": ["90aae1fda3666fcfba41a833fa4a278a6dae3b2d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Edouard Oger \u003ceoger@fastmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1484059 p1 - Pass both the profile name and the profile dir in initGecko() r=jchen a=pascalc\n\nGeckoProfile.initFromArgs is called using the values set in initGecko.\ninitFromArgs will then only recognize a profileDir, leave profileName null,\nand then call GeckoProfile.get who will then create a \"Custom (anonymous)\nprofile with specified dir.\" type of GeckoProfile, which is incorrect.\nWe fix the profile by specifying both -profile and -P in the args string.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D7671", "files": ["mobile/android/base/java/org/mozilla/gecko/GeckoService.java"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cfaf1ec5c361acbfb7d637ca9630a8a77d0d4b48", "parents": 